summary: A strange girl, with no home.
descriptionHtml:
My first Mod!

You need to spawn her using console:
help 4 Mystery
Find Mystery Girl and type player.placeatme (Code after name) 1

She is currently unkillable, (Doesnt lose health) tell me if you want a killable version.

She is set to be marryable, no idea if it works though. Report back in comments?

manual install: Put the BSA and ESP file into your skyrim/data folder
Automatic: Use Nexus Mod Manager.
author: Robertmanbob
